      • handleTilt

        public void handleTilt(boolean goingUp,
                       double tiltTolerance,
                       double tiltAdjustment)
        Method to set output ranges of piston controllers in response to an input of tilt adjustment. Will do nothing if the NavX is not connected!
        Parameters:
        goingUp - True if robot is climbing up and false if coming down
        tiltTolerance - The tolerance past which the robot is considered too unbalanced in either direction
        tiltAdjustment - The amount of adjustment desired for the robot
